SECURITY NOTICE:

This software is provided as a security tool to help developers detect and
prevent the accidental exposure of secrets and sensitive data. While we have
taken great care to ensure the security and privacy of this tool:

- All scanning happens locally on your machine
- No data is ever sent to external servers
- No telemetry or tracking is included
- Your code and secrets remain private

However, no security tool is perfect. Users are responsible for:

- Proper configuration and use of the tool
- Rotating any detected credentials
- Implementing comprehensive security practices
- Regular security audits and reviews

The authors and copyright holders shall not be liable for any data breaches,
security incidents, or damages that may occur from the use or misuse of this
software.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. ALWAYS IMPLEMENT DEFENSE IN DEPTH.
